## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-----------|--------|------------|
| Header scrolling with columns | Low | Medium | Verify DOM structure, restructure if needed |
| Preference not persisting | Low | Low | Zustand persist middleware handles this automatically |
| Drag-drop breaks with scrolling | Low | High | Test thoroughly, DnD should work with overflow |
| Performance issues with many columns | Low | Low | Width calculation is simple, no perf concern |

