## Edge Cases

1. **Very narrow viewports (mobile):** Preference should still apply, but may force horizontal scroll even with 1 column
2. **visibleColumns > total columns:** Show all columns evenly distributed (no scrolling)
3. **visibleColumns = total columns:** Show all columns evenly distributed (no scrolling)
4. **Invalid preference value:** Fallback to default (5)

